  "riddle": "1. In the heartland, trace your steps to a Midwestern town, known by the surname of an iconic American pioneer. From its Wikipedia page, tally the number of inhabitants as of the year that saw a leap in decimal places.\n\n2. To reach new heights, uncover how far above the oceans the soil stands in this same land of pioneers. Determine its position from a bird's eye view.\n\n3. Hungry adventurers would seek out local eateries. Quantify these culinary choices you might find scattered across this Midwest settlement.\n\n4. Take the lofty figure you previously unearthed and blend it with your recent culinary tally. What sum do these figures compose?\n\n5. Venturing north of this town, explore a broader entity of politics and plains. This sprawling state's dimensions are quantified in thousands of square kilometers—seek this number.\n\n6. From a page devoted to a biblical figure of paternal lineage and divine acceptance, count the distinct sections that divide the tale.\n\n7. The numerical beauty lies in simplicity — from the sections you just counted, distill it down by gathering all singular digits into a harmonious sum.\n\n8. Now a challenge of absolute measure awaits. Using values from the heights of the pioneer land and the sum you just concocted, subtract and prepare for a modern digit dance. Compute the absolute remainder when crisscrossed paths are distilled through ten.\n\nIn this exploration, you are tasked to compute using the values from clues 2, 4, and 6. What single numeral emerges from your calculations?",
